Place PWA icon files here:

  icon-192.png  — 192x192 px, referenced by manifest.json
  icon-512.png  — 512x512 px, referenced by manifest.json

Both should use "purpose": "any maskable" so they work on Android
adaptive icon circles and iOS home screen rounding.

Quick generation from a single source PNG (requires ImageMagick):
  convert source.png -resize 192x192 icon-192.png
  convert source.png -resize 512x512 icon-512.png
